<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.2">
<l>vētattai  vētat tiṉcuvaip payaṉai</l>
<l>viḻumiya muṉivarkaḷ viḻuṅkum</l>
<l>kōtiliṉ kaṉiyai nantaṉār kaḷiṟṟaik</l>
<l>kuvalayat tōrtoḻu tēttu</l>
<l>mātiyai yamutai yeṉṉaiyā ḷuṭai</l>
<l>yappaṉai yoppava rillā</l>
<l>mātarkaḷ vāḻum māṭamā mayilait</l>
<l>tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[The one who is] the Vedas, the sweet reward of the Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">the spotless fruit that eminent sages devour,</l>
<l>Nanda’s bull elephant, the primal lord</l>
<l rend="indent">whom those of the world praise and worship,</l>
<l>[My] ambrosia, father who governs me, I saw in Tiruvallikkēṇi</l>
<l>In great Māyilai, with mansions where matchless maids dwell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
